{"tid":914883,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母揸的士就咪撚向的士裡面食煙","createTime":"2018-11-24T15:18:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-24T17:05:08.000Z","uid":5584,"like":33,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ad1439a35656c5a5f1f1edf378e2a7fc23b30d2e","tid":914883,"uid":5584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T15:18:05.000Z","msg":"你仲夠贍掉煙頭落地下<br />\n我真係屌你老母都浪費我時間<br />\n全程的士我忍你<br />\n我一粒聲都冇出過<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因為我上網填緊表格，篤緊你灰呀，你乖乖地罰1500喇</span></span>"},{"pid":"dbf5a875ca761e19ae3a45fd3b1e014bc2c20bb0","tid":914883,"uid":5584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T15:26:12.000Z","msg":"啲的士佬真係好撚倡狂"},{"pid":"41513a6f3891349a0416d2fc4d2325b00ae71eb5","tid":914883,"uid":106544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T15:30:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b11521d918af32df8c8e08e552783fc411f9c6dc","tid":914883,"uid":5584,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T15:32:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.fehd.gov.hk/english/forms/fehb10.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fehd.gov.hk%2Fenglish%2Fforms%2Ffehb10.pdf&d=uA%2FGo34BWxrBAzh9DwwTaZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=3f1c9a5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.fehd.gov.hk/english/forms/fehb10.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n篤灰表格"},{"pid":"87f44d51c1db79e4dc91407859e8c7ade27ef59d","tid":914883,"uid":7314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T15:39:06.000Z","msg":"認真問<br />\n<br />\n的士佬唔認既話<br />\n仲鋤唔鋤到佢呢"},{"pid":"a282cb53f27249ca30fa9ff167569e47c8e19cb1","tid":914883,"uid":5584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87f44d51c1db79e4dc91407859e8c7ade27ef59d","tid":914883,"uid":7314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T15:39:06.000Z","msg":"認真問<br />\n<br />\n的士佬唔認既話<br />\n仲鋤唔鋤到佢呢"},"citedBy":1,"re